# Installation

## Install as extension package (`owi-metadatabase-{{ project_slug }}`)

```bash
pip install owi-metadatabase-{{ project_slug }}
```

Using `uv`:

```bash
uv pip install owi-metadatabase-{{ project_slug }}
```

## Install from core package extra (`owi-metadatabase[{{ project_slug }}]`)

If you prefer installing from the base package extras:

```bash
pip install "owi-metadatabase[{{ project_slug }}]"
```

Using `uv`:

```bash
uv pip install "owi-metadatabase[{{ project_slug }}]"
```

## Development setup

```bash
uv sync --dev
```
